OL,7,GFull restoration of Freeview signals
OL,8,Gin North East England moved a step
OL,9,Gcloser this week after the final
OL,10,Gstage of the structural phase of the
OL,11,Gconstruction of a new transmitter
OL,12,Gmast to serve the area was completed.
OL,14,FA new 300 metre high mast has been
OL,15,Fbuilt on Bilsdale West Moor on the
OL,16,Fsite of the original mast, which had
OL,17,Fto be demolished in 2021 after a fire
OL,18,Fseverely damaged the structure,
OL,19,Fknocking out TV, radio and mobile
OL,20,Fsignals in the area.
OL,3,CBilsdale transmitter mast
OL,4,Cconstruction complete: time to add
OL,5,Cthe broadcasting equipment
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/5
