OL,7,FWork is now underway to add the
OL,8,Fbroadcasting equipment up the sides
OL,9,Fand the top of the mast, including
OL,10,Fthe antenna that will transmit
OL,11,FFreeview TV services across North
OL,12,FYorkshire, County Durham and Teesside.
OL,14,FOnce complete, the existing network
OL,15,Fof temporary masts, including the
OL,16,Finterim Bilsdale Tower can be turned
OL,17,Foff.
OL,19,FArqiva, the owners and operators of
OL,20,FBilsdale mast, is on track to
OL,21,Fcomplete the necessary installation
OL,22,Fbefore the end of spring 2023.
OL,3,CBilsdale transmitter mast
OL,4,Cconstruction complete: time to add
OL,5,Cthe broadcasting equipment
