OL,7,FIn 2022, Ofcom blasted Arqiva for not
OL,8,Fhaving site-specific plans for
OL,9,Femergencies at Bilsdale. An
OL,10,Finvestigation into the aftermath of
OL,11,Fthe incident also found
OL,12,Fcommunications from Arqiva to
OL,13,Fstakeholders and viewers was lacking.
OL,15,FA survey commissioned by Ofcom found
OL,16,Fonly 4% had received any help from
OL,17,Fthe support scheme launched in the
OL,18,Faftermath to help viewers restore
OL,19,Ftheir TV service.
